{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "11.0",
      "line_index": 11,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9e5ca923",
      "speaker": "少女",
      "ja": "はぁっ、はぁっ、はぁっ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "13.0",
      "line_index": 13,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "52e321b4",
      "speaker": "少女",
      "ja": "なンデ、なンデ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "15.0",
      "line_index": 15,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "beb3976d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "深い森の中を、枝で足が切れることも厭わず少女が走り抜ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "19.0",
      "line_index": 19,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "27fb6888",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "枝から枝へ、岩から岩へと飛び移り、まるで風のように飛び回る少女だが、前方に別の影が立ちはだかった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "21.0",
      "line_index": 21,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a6d71bf3",
      "speaker": "少女",
      "ja": "っ…………！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "23.0",
      "line_index": 23,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8668bd8",
      "speaker": "武装した男",
      "ja": "逃げるナ。自分の使命を忘れたカ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.0",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c7f72de8",
      "speaker": "少女",
      "ja": "しっ……使命なんて、知らナイ！　急になンデ、こンナ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "29.0",
      "line_index": 29,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7db29c20",
      "speaker": "武装した少女",
      "ja": "……好きに抵抗するがいい。死への抗い、生への執着……神が最も欲する、我らの営みの一部である",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "31.0",
      "line_index": 31,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "69de3fc0",
      "speaker": "少女",
      "ja": "ひっ…………！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "34.0",
      "line_index": 34,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "76933e8",
      "speaker": "武装した少女",
      "ja": "それも、ここまでのようだが。……貴様は贄に選ばれたのだ。運命を受け入れるがいい",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.0",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "55403193",
      "speaker": "少女",
      "ja": "いっ…………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.0",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "766581a8",
      "speaker": "少女",
      "ja": "いやあっ…………！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "68.0",
      "line_index": 68,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3ea6335e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "う……ううう……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "70.0",
      "line_index": 70,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d0f9eace",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ふ、不時着ってなんだよ……すげえ衝撃だったぞ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "77.1",
      "line_index": 77,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7e986651",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "い、たたあ……だ、大丈夫だった？　{G_PlayerName}？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.0",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d51fa0d2",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "な、なんとか……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "88.1",
      "line_index": 88,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6b1318d1",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ル、ルミナ様！　お怪我はございませんか！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "90.1",
      "line_index": 90,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "4b6d24a3",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "う、うん……大丈夫……雫は？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "92.1",
      "line_index": 92,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "84c594a1",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "私の心配などなさらないでください。……それより、アポロ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "100.1",
      "line_index": 100,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "4ae4938a",
      "speaker": "アポロ",
      "ja": "ワタシは失敗していません。最良の操縦によって無事に着陸に成功しています。あとアポロではなくAPL-180です",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "102.1",
      "line_index": 102,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d664b453",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "無事、とは言いますが……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "104.0",
      "line_index": 104,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e494db6c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "周囲を見回す。小さい飾りなどが倒れてはいるが、確かに大きい家具などの様子は変わっていない。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "106.0",
      "line_index": 106,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b2266f06",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "……と言っても、固定されているだけだろうが。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "108.1",
      "line_index": 108,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e724a371",
      "speaker": "アポロ",
      "ja": "当機体の状態も問題ございません。自己修復プログラムを起動し、修理が完了すればいつでも飛び立てます",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "110.0",
      "line_index": 110,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b686dcc5",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "それは問題があるってことじゃないのか……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "112.1",
      "line_index": 112,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "30b0c97b",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "……であれば、しばらくここに留まるということですね。周囲の安全を確認しに……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "115.1",
      "line_index": 115,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "9e01d2e1",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "いっ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "117.1",
      "line_index": 117,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a164d0ac",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "雫！　……まだ体、痛むの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.1",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "dcb86733",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "も、問題ございません。確かに戦闘は出来ないかも知れませんが、周囲の確認程度であれば……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.1",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e540b9ff",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "ダメ！　……ごめんね、{G_PlayerName}くん、コハルさん。……お願いしたいんだけれど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "129.1",
      "line_index": 129,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "39a7772a",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "周りの安全を確認してくればいいのね？　勿論、大丈夫！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.1",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2008bf7f",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "……雫だけじゃなくて、ルミナも……大丈夫なの？　顔色真っ白だけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "133.1",
      "line_index": 133,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e79447df",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "う……うん。ごめんなさい……ちょっと、気分が悪い……かも……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "135.0",
      "line_index": 135,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a44decb9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "強がってばかりいたルミナが、珍しく素直に体の不調を口にする。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "137.0",
      "line_index": 137,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a48541a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "グリムとグレアとかいう王女候補が来たことが、相当負担になってしまったようだ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.1",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5d734799",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "うん、無理しないで。……雫も、それでいい？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "141.1",
      "line_index": 141,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "19704002",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "願ってもないことですが……危険を感じたらすぐに戻ってきてください。男はさておき……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "143.0",
      "line_index": 143,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "eba9a0a2",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "おい！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "145.1",
      "line_index": 145,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "dc6b9636",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "まあ、私は微塵も気にしませんが、ルミナ様が悲しみます。無事に戻れたら戻ってきなさい",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "147.0",
      "line_index": 147,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a258876b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "はあ…………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "149.1",
      "line_index": 149,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e78fbfc1",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "じゃ、{G_PlayerName}。気をつけて行きましょ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "151.0",
      "line_index": 151,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e1699a34",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ああ。変な動物とか出ないといいけどな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "159.1",
      "line_index": 159,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c676a85d",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ふふっ、{G_PlayerName}？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "161.0",
      "line_index": 161,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "255467e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ん？　なんだよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "163.1",
      "line_index": 163,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "efa76ced",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "なんかハチャメチャだけど、２人っきりの冒険が始まるみたいで、ワクワクしない？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.0",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "99019ded",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……確かに。これぞ冒険って感じだな",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "184.0",
      "line_index": 184,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "518eb37b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "う…………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "186.1",
      "line_index": 186,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a9e87af4",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "うわああ…………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "188.0",
      "line_index": 188,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "67580eba",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "見渡す限りの樹木。見上げれば甲高い鳥の鳴き声が響き、歩けば小さな虫が足元から離れてゆく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "190.1",
      "line_index": 190,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "35838bca",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ぼ、冒険……って感じだけど……ねぇ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "192.0",
      "line_index": 192,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9fa2d4a0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "お、おう……武者震いするな",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "194.0",
      "line_index": 194,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1504c775",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "周囲の安全を確認するだけとは言え、絵に描いたような未開の地に気圧されてしまう。ムンと立ち込める草いきれが、冷や汗の流れた頬を撫ぜた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "196.1",
      "line_index": 196,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "3434a6bd",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "し……慎重に行くわよ！　あたしが前、あんたは後ろ！　いいわね？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "198.0",
      "line_index": 198,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bf68e1ea",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "わかった……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "205.1",
      "line_index": 205,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2c168549",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ちょっといいですか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "209.1",
      "line_index": 209,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "452f8690",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "きゃーーーっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "212.0",
      "line_index": 212,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b9ed4a60",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うわあああああっ！？　びっくりしたっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "214.1",
      "line_index": 214,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a7d9e373",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "な、なんですか！　びっくりしたのはこっちです！　先が思いやられますね！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "216.1",
      "line_index": 216,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ce6096f1",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "で、出てきて大丈夫なの？　休んでたほうが……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "218.1",
      "line_index": 218,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2fd32e36",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ご心配なく。これを渡しに来ただけです",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "220.0",
      "line_index": 220,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "440c4c01",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そう言って、雫が何か四角くて小さい鉄の箱のような物を手渡す。表面に、赤いボタンのような物があるようだが……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "222.0",
      "line_index": 222,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "45bd377c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "これは……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "224.1",
      "line_index": 224,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7090d63",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "なんと言えば伝わるか……危機が訪れたら押してください。救援装置のような物です",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "226.1",
      "line_index": 226,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c77c1d75",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ふうん……？　どうも……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "228.1",
      "line_index": 228,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "9b47b1ec",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "では、お気をつけて",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "236.1",
      "line_index": 236,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e9b2251f",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "じゃ、じゃあ出鼻をくじかれたけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "238.0",
      "line_index": 238,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d11d7865",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "進むとするか……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "246.0",
      "line_index": 246,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2914052",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "不安とちょっとした興奮を抑えながら、コハルとの初めての冒険は始まった……",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
